name: tilelive-s3simple
readme:
# tilelive-s3simple

Reads/writes tiles and grids from/to AWS s3. This module is intended to be used with [tilelive.js](https://github.com/mapbox/tilelive.js).
description: Reads/writes tiles and grids from/to AWS s3. This module is intended to be used with [tilelive.js](https://github.com/mapbox/tilelive.js).
